DB-to-DB Migration Architecture (Huge Load)
This is the most common real-world Spring Batch use case — moving millions of rows from a source DB to a target DB with transformation in between.
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│              DB TO DB MIGRATION — HIGH LEVEL FLOW                       │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘

  SOURCE DB (Oracle / MySQL / PostgreSQL)
       │
       │  JdbcPagingItemReader / JdbcCursorItemReader
       │  reads in pages (e.g. 1000 rows per page)
       ▼
